tery behind why they were incarcerated in the first place.\n\nWhile the game is best experienced with team, you are free to tackle the mission on your own. Choose any rodent and use your wits to escape the prison!", "short_description": "Rodent People: Origins is a multiplayer VR escape room, in which teams of up to 4 players use their wits and cooperation to solve innovative, story driven puzzles to try and break out of a prison cell playing as the incarcerated rats - the Rodent People."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.privacypolicies.com/live/ebcd8408-709b-4e98-bc3e-37bbdecacc76", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Zen Republic", "support_website_url": "Http://www.zenrepublic.space/contacthq", "website_url": "Http://www.zenrepublic.space/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "377978390272490"}, {"id": "2691890164460465"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PUZZLE", "ADVENTURE", "SHOOTER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["CO_OP", "SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "643327726866528"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "6558942254177010", "version": "v0.70"}, "id": "256960702660350", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "